{
  "texts": [
    "It provides rich and extensive data that facilitates in-depth analysis of human opinions and sentiments.",
    "In A-Learn, we scrap plenty of comments related to adult learning from multiple social media platforms, including Reddit, Twitter, and Tumblr.",
    "They are selected because of their diverse user demographics (e.g.",
    "various age groups and backgrounds) and well-supported APIs.",
    "Our comment search is based on keywords such as adult learning, part-time studies, continuous learning, and work study."
  ]
}